                        <interp inst="t18640104-name-170" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD BARLOW</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Solomon, Gray's-Inn-road—I produce a pair of boots pledged in the name of Lambert, between 10 and 11 o'clock, 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi> December.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18640104-name-171" type="witnessName">
