                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Reeve, 13, Red Cross-street—I produce two pairs of boots, pledged on the 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi> December, in the morning, by a man, in the name of Lambert.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18640104-name-172" type="witnessName">
