                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Richard Attenborough, of Fins<lb></lb>bury—I produce a pair of boots pledged, on 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi> December, about 2 o'clock, by a man, in the name of Smith.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18640104-name-173" type="witnessName">
