                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. John Russell, 27, Fore-street—I produce a pair of boots pledged about 12 o'clock, on 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi> December, by a woman for 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18640104-name-174" type="witnessName">
