                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Folker, of Gray's-Inn-road—I produce a pair of boots pledged in the name of John Lambert, on 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi> De<lb></lb>cember, about half-past 10 in the morning, for 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186401040035"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18640104-name-175" type="witnessName">
