                        <interp inst="t18640104-name-175" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY STOKES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). All these boots are mine—I have looked at them all before—they all have my initials on them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Thompson.</hi> I wanted the sergeant who apprehended the woman. He is not here; it was a sergeant in private clothes.</p>
