                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Thompson was further charged with having been before convicted of felony at this Court, on 18th August</hi>, 1862, <hi rend="italic">in the name of John Read, to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. †—<hi rend="italic">
